        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The prophet makes an Athletics check to Grab a creature he is touching. A creature he @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabs} is exposed to <strong>Filth Fever</strong> (@Check[type:fortitude|dc:16]): on a failure it is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 1} (Sickened 2 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 1} on a critical failure); the disease advances daily until cured.</p>"
        },
