      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> a doomsayer, not a real fight — the danger is the <strong>Filth Fever</strong> he carries, contracted if he Grabs a PC. Most prophets are harmless street-corner prognosticators; this one has fixated on a PC.</p><p><strong>Behavior:</strong> raves and reaches for the PC he is obsessed with; flees or collapses once struck. Curing his disease (or his madness) is a Good deed, not an XP-for-kill.</p>",
